--====================================================================
-- Gamepasses side button + Spawner  (LocalScript, Roblox Studio)
-- Place in: StarterPlayer > StarterPlayerScripts
--
-- Studio-only build (no executor functions). Auto-accept uses
-- VirtualInputManager, which works in Studio play-tests only.
--
-- Behaviour:
--   * The spawner menu is ALWAYS visible; press ] to toggle it on/off.
--   * Gamepasses starts UNSELECTED. Click it -> green, other side buttons
--     turn 64/86/97, and the spawner's created panels show.
--   * Clicking any other side button hides everything the spawner created.
--====================================================================

